videos.description: Tosan Evbuomwan hit a last-second shot with 4.8 seconds remaining to lift Princeton to a 74-73 win at Harvard. With the win, the Tigers clinched at least a share of the title.
videos.headline: Princeton Outlasts Harvard, 74-73  - Via Ivy League
